                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-626-18560616 t18560616-626-punishment-52"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There was another indicment against the prisoner.</hi>)</p>
